At long last, new Ad Astra Per Aspera content.

If anybody is curious this is based on the Pioneer anomaly, a phenomenon with a name so perfect that I just had to write something based on it. However, the actual explanation behind the anomaly is cool enough that I had to preserve it to some degree. That meant shelving the anomalous shenanigans on Pioneer 11 rather than both probes. (Pioneer 10 gets to live, for now)

Thanks to Nyaaly for crit!

